prompt.title: Embedding for Introducing Book: Markdown-Inspired AI Language
prompt.content: The Book language is based on markdown, designed to be easily readable by both humans and machines. It uses .book file extension and UTF-8 encoding. It has two variants: flat (single prompt) and full (structured with tasks, commands, and prompts).
